name.k: ナイティナイト　リトルシープ!

platformAttributes.ios.subtitle.k: 儿童的睡前故事应用程序
こども向けベッドタイム・ストーリー アプリ

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.ta.k: 温馨睡前故事 与可爱动物一起入眠

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: This charming bedtime story will soothe your young child with delightful imagery and a simple but engaging spoken tale. Inside an exquisitely illustrated farmhouse, adorable woodland animals need help turning out the lights to fall asleep. Intuitive controls and fun interactive surprises make Nighty Night a pleasure to explore, and with optional narration, you and your toddler can settle in to be entertained or bring your own imaginations to the wonderful nighttime world.
